        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Nov. 5</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I thank you for your <hi rend="underline">extremely</hi> kind note &amp; granting of my request so promptly.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/> I will write this evening to M<hi rend="superscript">ess</hi>. Appleton.—<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p>
<p>I am sorry about Expression book as by your previous note— It is a bad job, but I still think the book will sell in the course of years, though this of course a heavy loss.—<ref target="#foot.f4"/></p>
<p>Yours very sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="tnotes">
                <note xml:id="tnote.n1">1.1 your] <hi rend="italic">interl</hi> </note>
                <note xml:id="tnote.n2">1.1 so promptly.] <hi rend="italic">interl above caret altered from point</hi> </note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

