            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Murray’s note has not been found.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-9713.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to D. Appleton &amp; Co., 5 November 1874</ref>.</note>
